Tga '''Taydrt n uswingm''' yat tmzgunt n taydrt n uswingm, n umara d umdyaz [[Lmsɛudi Muḥmmad]] s tutlayt tamaziɣt, tg zɣ tiẓṛigin n tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt. iffaɣ d usnflul asklan ad ɣ usggʷas n 2019.

Tga tmzgunt ad asnflul asklan wis sin dar umara, ig udlis n tmzgunt amṛwaṣu, isman udlis 90 n talɣa, ma ittggan 45 n tnfult, ilin t gis snat tmzgunin n wazzann, ttyarant s uskkil n [[Tifinaɣ|tfinaɣ]] d uskkil n [[Agmmay alatin n tmaziɣt|tlatinit]].

Tawlaft n udmawn n udlis tẓli tnt tzlɣa n tirra n imaratn s tmaziɣt, tg i udm amzwaru aklu umlil ɣ llan kṛaḍ ijjign n tafukt, d yan [[Agḍiḍ|ugḍiḍ]], yili f udm amzwaru n udlis assaɣ n umara d tamatart n tzlɣa n tirra, ittyura fllas uzwl n tmzgunt s uskkil n [[Tifinaɣ|tfinaɣ]] d uskkil [[Agmmay alatin n tmaziɣt|alatini]]. ɣ udm wis sin, iṭṭf aklu azggʷaɣ, tili fllas tawlaft n umara, d twwuriwin nns tisnflulin, ili gis ula atig n udlis igan 30 n drhm.

